PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 45 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding which occured in PRINCE EDWARD ISLAND on January 21, 2000, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in that regard.
